== Original Projects 

=> Stay tuned for more useful info here ...

=> Steps for setting up development database:

   1) cp config/database.example config/database.yml # Edit database.yml as required
   2) rake db:migrate # create the tables
   3) rake db:seed    # loadup the bootstrap database
   4) rake thinking_sphinx:index  # create the sphinx indices
   5) rake thinking_sphinx:start  # startup sphinx searchd

=> For checking working in progress test cases:

   1) git checkout code_coverage
   2) rake test   # for running all test cases
   OR
   3) rake test:coverage  # for running testcases and generating rcov report
   
   Note: very soon code_coverage will be merged with master.
